    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "While including resolution in sys info would be useful in some cases, I am not sure why it should be a reason to decide whether https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/12629 should be done or not. You recently did HiDPI support and you didn't base that off any statistics, so why suddenly do it for here? I have a 4K display and the UI is pretty small on my screen, so I think doing some type of UI scale would be nice to have."
